                    <span>Cisco IOS in a Nutshell is a good book for Cisco students and admininstrators alike. It is a good reference to keep by your router if you need to get the gist of certain commands. Mr. Boney does a good job explaining Cisco technologies.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">CISCO IOS in a nutshell</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
                      /
                      <span>0</span>
